## Windsurf AI Development Rules

### Stack: {{stack}}

- Next.js 15 App Router — `app/page.tsx`, `app/layout.tsx`
- Server Components first — `'use client'` only for interactivity
- Data fetching in Server Components, Server Actions for mutations
- Route handlers in `app/api/`
- Test: Vitest + @testing-library/react + jsdom
- Tip: Next.js caches aggressively — use `revalidate`/`force-dynamic` explicitly
